{"lemma":"زِرٌّ","slug":"زِرٌّ","root":"ز.ر.ر","root_slug":"ز-ر-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ز-ر-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"زِرٌّ","root":"زور","pos":"V","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":9},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n17614"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B2%D9%90%D8%B1%D9%8C%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to encroach upon one's enemy"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to apprehend, to perceive"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to beam, to dazzle, to gleam, to glitter"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to button"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to collect intensely"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to constrict"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to blanch, to bleach, to dust off"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"button"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"switch button in a power socket"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n17614","headword_ar":"زِرٌّ","root":"zr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Msb, K, &c.,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zur~N","text_ar":"زُرٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (ISk,) app. in the same sense, (Az,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zar~N","text_ar":"زَرٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"has been also mentioned, but this is doubtful, (MF,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A button"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, A, Msb, TA) of a shirt, (IAar, S, A, Msb, K,) and of other things, as, for instance, of a curtain: (MF, TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"loop into which a button is put:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISh:) the latter, accord. to Az, is the right meaning: (TA:) [but the former is that to which the word is generally applied:] the former is also called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ziyrN","text_ar":"زِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", by a change of the first"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"r","text_ar":"ر"},{"kind":"text","text":": (IAar:) pl. [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^azoraArN","text_ar":"اَزْرَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb, K) and [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zuruwrN","text_ar":"زُرُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) [Hence the saying,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa A^alozamu liY","text_ar":"هُوَ اَلْزَمُ لِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino zir~iY liEurowatihi","text_ar":"مِنْ زِرِّى لِعُرْوَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is more fast to me than my button to its loop"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoTaAniyhi bizir~ihi","text_ar":"اَعْطَانِيهِ بِزِرِّهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave it to me altogether."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alz~ir~u","text_ar":"الزِّرُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The star"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ξ","text_ar":"ξ","orth_type":"plain"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of Gemini;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one of the two stars called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlhanoEapu","text_ar":"الهَنْعَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Kzw.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zir~N","text_ar":"زِرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain piece of wood at the upper extremity of the pole of a tent:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K: *) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^azoraArN","text_ar":"اَزْرَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the upper end of the tent-pole is inserted into it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) or the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AzrAr","text_ar":"ازرار"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a tent ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xibaA='","text_ar":"خِبَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":") are"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"certain pieces of wood which are sewed into the upper parts of the pieces of cloth which compose the tent, the lower ends of which"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pieces of cloth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"are upon the ground:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zar~ahaA","text_ar":"زَرَّهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies “ he made in them [namely the said pieces of cloth] such pieces of wood. ” (TA.) ―         -b4-  (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"socket in which the head of the upper bone of the arm turns;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K; *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resembling the half of a nut:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"head itself of that bone:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extremity of the hip-bone, in the socket."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b5-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain small bone,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resembling the half of a nut,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, [but this is probably a misplaced insertion, from the A, ubi suprà,])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beneath the heart, of which it is the support."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b6-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The edge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"each of the two edges,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) of a sword. (IAar, K, TA.) ―         -b7-  One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahu lazir~N mino A^azoraAri AlA_ibili","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُ لَزِرٌّ مِنْ اَزْرَارِ الاـِبِلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * A, K *) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily he is one who keeps close to the camels;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a good pastor of them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K. [Accord. to the A, it seems to be from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zir~N","text_ar":"زِرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying “ a button. ”]) You term also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zir~u maAlK","text_ar":"زِرُّ مَالٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One who drives camels,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like, vehemently;"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to some; but the preceding meaning, given in the K, is the more correct: (TA:) or it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one acquainted with the right management thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who manages them well;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAlK","text_ar":"مَالٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zurozuwru","text_ar":"زُرْزُورُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zir~u Ald~iyni","text_ar":"زِرُّ الدِّينِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The support,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prop, of the religion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Abu-l-'Abbás, K;) like the small bone called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zir~","text_ar":"زِرّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is the support of the heart: (Abu-l-'Abbás, TA:) applied, in a trad., to 'Alee: in another relation, it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zir~u AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"زِرُّ الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he between whom and the earth is a mutual dependance, and without whose existence one would repudiate the earth and mankind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, accord. to Th,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he by whom the earth becomes firm, like as a shirt does by means of its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zir~","text_ar":"زِرّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"button"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["ISk","Az","MF","IAar","A","Msb","TA","S","K","ISh","L"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}